AppJ[ ]:::junctionStyle
BotJ[ ]:::junctionStyle
ObsJ[ ]:::junctionStyle

%% ── Rank Controls (Vertical Ordering) ────────────────────────────────────
%% Use subgraph direction TB to enforce layout; no invisible edges needed

%% ── Connections ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Browser -->|"HTTP REST · X-Session-ID header"| App
App -->|"JSON: message · stage · strategy · latency_ms · provider · model · training"| Browser

App --- AppJ
AppJ --> Sec
AppJ --> Bot
AppJ --> Trainer
AppJ --> Quiz
AppJ --> Prospect
AppJ --> Know
BotJ --> WebSearch
App -->|"QuickMatcher.match_product() on /api/init"| Loader

Bot --- BotJ
BotJ --> FSM
BotJ --> NLU
BotJ --> Factory
BotJ --> Ana
BotJ --> Perf

FSM --> Content
Content --> NLU
Content --> Loader
Loader --> F_Y

Factory --> ProvBase
ProvBase -->|"HTTPS · groq-sdk"| G
ProvBase -.->|"HTTPS · fallback on 429 or error"| OR
ProvBase -.->|"HTTPS · last resort"| SN

Ana --- ObsJ
Perf --- ObsJ
ObsJ -->|"append-only · threading.Lock"| F_J
Bot -->|"save_session()"| F_S

